(495, 1, '2015-03-10 09:20:28', '2015-03-10 09:20:28', '<div class="total_link_text">\r\n<div class="extrnl_tab_link">[sidebar name="The Area Menu Sidebar"]</div>\r\n<div class="right_text">[seven_twelfths]\r\n<h3>Driving Directions</h3>\r\n<b>From Austin:</b> <em>Approx. 65 miles / 1.25 hours by car</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on US 290 / TX-71 / Southwest Parkway heading West</li>\r\n	<li>Follow Southwest Parkway to TX-71 West for approx. 47 miles</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto RM 2233/RR 2233</li>\r\n	<li>Turn left onto RM 2900/RR 2900</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto FM 1431 East</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>From Dallas:</b> <em>Approx. 210 miles / 3.25 hours by car</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on I-35 East / South</li>\r\n	<li>Drive 144 miles and take exit 283 toward FM 2268 / FM 2843 / Holland</li>\r\n	<li>Take FM 2843 / TX-138 West / FM 243 West to FM 1431 West</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>From San Antonio:</b> <em>Approx. 97 miles / 1.75 hours by car</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on I-37 North</li>\r\n	<li>Get on US-281 North and take it FM 962 / RR 962 West in Round Mountain</li>\r\n	<li>Turn left onto TX-71 West</li>\r\n	<li>Take RR 2900 to FM 1431 East</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>From West Texas:</b> <em>Travel time and distance vary</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on I-35 East / South</li>\r\n	<li>Drive 144 miles and take exit 283 toward FM 2268 / FM 2843 / Holland</li>\r\n	<li>Take FM 2843 / TX-138 West / FM 243 West to FM 1431 West</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/seven_twelfths][five_twelfths_last]\r\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d27454.149205452995!2d-98.4454228!3d30.6686425!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x865afe559e1dc013%3A0x8b27484361fa7f2f!2sKingsland%2C+TX%2C+USA!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1428996395775" width="400" height="450" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\n[/five_twelfths_last]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Driving Directions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'driving-directions', '', '', '2015-04-14 07:32:14', '2015-04-14 07:32:14', '', 0, '