li>The Dog Fee and Damage Waiver that you will be asked to review and sign upon arrival does not cover any damage caused by dog(s).</li>\r\n<li>You must prevent dog(s) from producing excessive noise during your stay; noise complaints will result in either removal or boarding of dog(s).</li>\r\n<li>Neither the Property Owner nor Lake Me Away assumes any responsibility for illness or injury that may affect dog(s) while on the premises.</li></ol>\r\n<p>Lessee agrees with the Lake Me Away Pet Policy and understands that Lessee is responsible for any damages by dog(s). Lessee also agrees to pay, without dispute, any cleaning or repair costs judged necessary by Lake Me Away.\r\nDate:	_______  	Printed Name:	  ________________________\r\nSignature:    ______________________________________________\r\n</p>\r\n[/seven_twelfths]\r\n[five_twelfths_last]<a href="wp-content/uploads/2015/03/PetPolicy.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-785" src="wp-content/uploads/2015/03/PetPolicy-300x200.jpg" alt="PetPolicy" width="300" height="200" /></a>[/five_twelfths_last]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Pet Policy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '765-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-17 10:53:17', '2015-03-17 10:53:17', '', 765, '765-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
