0,800 feet. As one of the most popular lakes in Texas, it is perfect for a variety of water activities and an outdoor lifestyle!\r\n\r\n[/seven_twelfths][five_twelfths_last]<img class="aligncenter" src="wp-content/uploads/2012/12/HighlandLakes.GIF" alt="" />[/five_twelfths_last][/tab]\r\n[tab title="Map"][seven_twelfths]\r\n<h3>Map</h3>\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d27482.33310246459!2d-98.37808235!3d30.569311599999992!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x865b03c890b85f27%3A0x66ddc396f46f2257!2sLake+Lyndon+B+Johnson%2C+Texas%2C+USA!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1426165477704" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"></iframe>[/seven_twelfths][five_twelfths_last][/five_twelfths_last][/tab]\r\n[tab title="Driving Directions"][seven_twelfths]\r\n<h3>Driving Directions</h3>\r\n<b>From Austin:</b> Approx. 55 miles / 1.10 hour by car\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on TX-71 W</li>\r\n	<li>Drive approx. 55 miles</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto FM 2147 E</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>From Dallas:</b> Approx. 210 miles / 3.75 hours by car\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on I-35 E S</li>\r\n	<li>Get on US-67 S and take it 86 miles to TX-220 S in Erath County</li>\r\n	<li>Take a slight left onto TX-220 S</li>\r\n	<li>Follow US-281 S for 103 miles to FM 2147 W in Marble Falls</li>\r\n	<li>Continue on FM 2147 W</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>From San Antonio:</b> Approx. 98 miles / 2 hours by car\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Get on I-37 N</li>\r\n	<li>Get on US-281 N and take it 90 miles to TX-71 W</li>\r\n	<li>Get on TX-71 W to FM 2147 E</li>\r\n	<li>Turn right onto FM 2147 E</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/seven_twelfths][five_twelfths_last]<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d54964.66597827171!2d-98.378082!3d30.569312000000004!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x865b03c890b85f27%3A0x66ddc396f46f2257!2sLake+Lyndon+B+Johnson%2C+Texas%2C+USA!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1427870480218" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0"></iframe>[/five_twelfths_last][/tab][tab title="Local Weather"]\r\n<h3>Local Weather</h3>\r\nBelow is a monthly overview of the weather in the area based on data from Kingsland, Texas.\r\n\r\n[five_twelfths_last]<img class="aligncenter" src="wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Weather.png" alt="" />[/five_twelfths_last][button url="http://www.weather.com/weather/today/l/30.56,-98.35?lat=30.56&amp;lon=-98.35&amp;locale=en_US&amp;temp=f" size="medium" target="_blanck"]Current Weather[/button][/tab][/tabs]', 'THE AREA', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '489-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-01 06:54:49', '2015-04-01 06:54:49', '', 489, '489-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
