(1006, 1, '2015-04-15 00:49:15', '2015-04-15 00:49:15', '<div class="total_link_text">\r\n<div class="extrnl_tab_link">[sidebar name="Rental menu sidebar"]</div>\r\n<div class="right_text">\r\n<h3>Rental Agreement</h3>\r\nThank you for your interest in renting a vacation home through Lake Me Away!\r\n\r\nWe are excited about your stay. Upon arrival, you will be asked to sign our standard Rental Agreement. If you wish to review in advance, please <a href="wp-content/uploads/2015/04/LMA_Rental_Agreement.pdf" target="_blank">download the Rental Agreement</a> now.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Rental Agreement', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '478-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-15 00:49:15', '2015-04-15 00:49:15', '', 478, '478-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1007, 1, '2015-04-15 00:52:11', '2015-04-15 00:52:11', '<div class="total_link_text">\r\n<div class="extrnl_tab_link">[sidebar name="Your Property sidebar"]</div>\r\n<div class="right_text">\r\n<h3>Why should Lake Me Away manage my home?</h3>\r\nLake Me Away is a professional management company owned and operated by experienced business leaders with specialties in luxury hospitality, sales and marketing and business. We believe wonderful vacation experiences in a lovely, lakeside setting create lifelong memories and we know that delivering those experiences is a worthwhile and rewarding art. We believe that the investor who is willing to offer their property to vacationing guests should be rewarded with a well cared for home and profitable investment. Lake Me Away will ensure a wonderful guest experience and profitable vacation home ownership. We pride ourselves on delivering high quality guest and owner services in a prompt and professional manner.\r\nWhat services will Lake Me Away provide?\r\n<ul class="first_dot">\r\n	<li><b>Marketing</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nProfessional property listings including the following:\r\n<ul class="first_dot">\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n<ul class="third_sqare">\r\n	<li>Showcasing high-quality photographs</li>\r\n	<li>Writing compelling property descriptions</li>\r\n	<li>Manage exposure by listing property on popular vacation websites such as VRBO.com, HomeAway.com, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\nData insights and optimization including the following:\r\n<ul class="first_dot">\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n<ul class="third_sqare">\r\n	<li>Using statistical analysis and guest relationships to increase repeat bookings</li>\r\n	<li>Using market data to analyze revenue trends and propose seasonal rate structures</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n	<li><b>Rental Logistics</b>\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>Reservations (see more below)</li>\r\n	<li>Payments</li>\r\n	<li>All guest communication from original inquiry to departure</li>\r\n	<li>Check-in and checkout processes</li>\r\n	<li>Welcoming guests to your home</li>\r\n	<li>Inspection and housekeeping services following departure</li>\r\n	<li>Light upkeep and maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Dispatch emergency maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Regular inspections of home</li>\r\n	<li>Establish and maintain relationships with local service partners</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><b>Reservations</b>\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>Manage rental availability calendars across multiple websites – VRBO, HA, LMA</li>\r\n	<li>Process credit cards and ACH check payments</li>\r\n	<li>Coordinate guest arrival and keys / codes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><b>Guest Relations</b>\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>Answer questions via email and / or phone prior to reservation and arrival, as well as post-departure</li>\r\n	<li>Survey guests regarding their stay and encourage online reviews</li>\r\n	<li>Build repeat visits</li>\r\n	<li>Address special requests from guests</li>\r\n	<li>Provide consumables when requested by Owner</li>\r\n	<li>Provide emergency maintenance assistance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><b>Owner Relations</b>\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>On-site maintenance of your investment – regular inspections, housekeeping, light maintenance, assistance with projects, deliveries, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Regular and timely monthly payment of collected rental fees</li>\r\n	<li>Monthly statements detailing rental and forfeit revenue from departed guests, as well as details of charges incurred such as commissions, taxes, cleaning fees or billable visits</li>\r\n	<li>Yield management analysis of rates and occupancy levels of your property against selected competitive properties to ensure maximum rentals and rate</li>\r\n	<li>(Optional) Assistance with errands, deliveries and other tasks as directed by the owner (Depending on the task, we charge a $20 fee to assist with smaller errands; Larger tasks such as painting, remodeling, etc. can certainly be discussed – we are happy to assist.)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>What are my responsibilities as a homeowner?</h3>\r\n<ul class="first_dot">\r\n	<li>Provide home for year-round rental pool</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure adequate homeowner’s property and liability insurance coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Provide a well-stocked home for guests including the following:\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>Furnishings</li>\r\n	<li>Towels and bath mats (two par level)</li>\r\n	<li>Sheets, blankets and pillows (two par level for sheets)</li>\r\n	<li>Kitchen supplies – cookware, utensils, glassware, plates, silverware, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Consumables – toilet paper, paper towels, dish soap, light bulbs, batteries, shampoo, bath soap (LMA can assist with stocking of consumables)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Ensure home is equipped with WI-FI and cable TV</li>\r\n	<li>Establish direct relationship with vendors, with LMA assistance if required, for repeat services such as lawn care, pest control, HVAC and pool maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Financial requirements:\r\n<ul class="second_circle">\r\n	<li>Initial set up of home including furnishings, linens, kitchen supplies, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Listings costs for VRBO.com and HomeAway.com</li>\r\n	<li>Direct billed services such as lawn care, pool care, HVAC service plan and pest control</li>\r\n	<li>Payment of all utilities, internet and cable costs</li>\r\n	<li>Recommended periodic maintenance such as gutter cleaning and window washing (twice per year)</li>\r\n	<li>Cleaning services for Owner or Friend use of property – billed on monthly statement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>What does Lake Me Away charge to manage my home?</h3>\r\nLake Me Away retains a 25% management fee on all rental revenues collected, including but not limited to, rentals completed, rental fees forfeited and pet fees collected. Merchant fees, as incurred by Lake Me Away, will be the Owner’s responsibility and deducted from rental proceeds.\r\n\r\n</div>\