educted from rental proceeds.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Owner FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '536-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-23 00:52:03', '2015-04-23 00:52:03', '', 536, '536-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
